<div class="c580_3">
<div id="v580.3.1"><span class="G1487 s">If</span><span class="G4891 s"> ye</span><span class="G3767 s"> then</span><span class="G4891 s"> be risen</span><span class="G5547 s"> with Christ</span><span class="G2212 s">, seek</span><span class="G507 s"> those things which are above</span><span class="G3757 s">, where</span><span class="G5547 s"> Christ</span><span class="G2076 s"> sitteth</span><span class="G1722 s"> G2521 on</span><span class="G1188 s"> the right hand</span><span class="G2316 s"> of God</span>.</div>
<div id="v580.3.2"><span class="G5426 s">Set your affection</span><span class="G507 s"> on things above</span><span class="G3361 s">, not</span><span class="G1909 s"> on things on</span><span class="G1093 s"> the earth</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (affection: or, mind)</span></div>
