<div id="v580.3.7"><span class="G1722 s">In</span><span class="G3739 s"> the which</span><span class="G5210 s"> ye</span><span class="G2532 s"> also</span><span class="G4043 s"> walked</span><span class="G4218 s"> some time</span><span class="G3753 s">, when</span><span class="G2198 s"> ye lived</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G846 s"> them</span>.</div>
