<div id="v580.3.9"><span class="G5574 s">Lie</span><span class="G3361 s"> not</span><span class="G1519 s"> one to another</span><span class="G554 s"> G240, seeing that ye have put off</span><span class="G3820 s"> the old</span><span class="G444 s"> man</span><span class="G4862 s"> with</span><span class="G846 s"> his</span><span class="G4234 s"> deeds</span>;</div>
<div id="v580.3.10"><span class="G2532 s">And</span><span class="G1746 s"> have put on</span><span class="G3501 s"> the new</span><span class="G3588 s"> <i>man</i>, which</span><span class="G341 s"> is renewed</span><span class="G1519 s"> in</span><span class="G1922 s"> knowledge</span><span class="G2596 s"> after</span><span class="G1504 s"> the image of him</span><span class="G2936 s"> that created</span><span class="G846 s"> him</span>:</div>
