<div id="v580.3.16"><span class="G1774 s">Let</span><span class="G3056 s"> the word</span><span class="G5547 s"> of Christ</span><span class="G1774 s"> dwell</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G5213 s"> you</span><span class="G4146 s"> richly</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G3956 s"> all</span><span class="G4678 s"> wisdom</span><span class="G1321 s">; teaching</span><span class="G2532 s"> and</span><span class="G3560 s"> admonishing</span><span class="G1438 s"> one another</span><span class="G5568 s"> in psalms</span><span class="G2532 s"> and</span><span class="G5215 s"> hymns</span><span class="G2532 s"> and</span><span class="G4152 s"> spiritual</span><span class="G5603 s"> songs</span><span class="G103 s">, singing</span><span class="G1722 s"> with</span><span class="G5485 s"> grace</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G5216 s"> your</span><span class="G2588 s"> hearts</span><span class="G2962 s"> to the Lord</span>.</div>
