<div id="v580.3.19"><span class="G435 s">Husbands</span><span class="G25 s">, love</span><span class="G1135 s"> <i>your</i> wives</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G4087 s"> be</span><span class="G3361 s"> not</span><span class="G4087 s"> bitter</span><span class="G4314 s"> against</span><span class="G846 s"> them</span>.</div>
