<div id="v580.3.21"><span class="G3962 s">Fathers</span><span class="G2042 s">, provoke</span><span class="G3361 s"> not</span><span class="G5216 s"> your</span><span class="G5043 s"> children</span><span class="G3363 s"> <i>to anger</i>, lest</span><span class="G120 s"> they be discouraged</span>.</div>
<div id="v580.3.22"><span class="G1401 s">Servants</span><span class="G5219 s">, obey</span><span class="G2596 s"> in</span><span class="G3956 s"> all things</span><span class="G2962 s"> <i>your</i> masters</span><span class="G2596 s"> according</span><span class="G4561 s"> to the flesh</span><span class="G3361 s">; not</span><span class="G1722 s"> with</span><span class="G3787 s"> eyeservice</span><span class="G5613 s">, as</span><span class="G441 s"> menpleasers</span><span class="G235 s">; but</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G572 s"> singleness</span><span class="G2588 s"> of heart</span><span class="G5399 s">, fearing</span><span class="G2316 s"> God</span>:</div>
<div id="v580.3.23"><span class="G2532 s">And</span><span class="G3956 s"> whatsoever</span><span class="G4160 s"> G3748 G1437 ye do</span><span class="G2038 s">, do</span><span class="G1537 s"> <i>it</i> heartily</span><span class="G5613 s"> G5590, as</span><span class="G2962 s"> to the Lord</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G3756 s"> not</span><span class="G444 s"> unto men</span>;</div>
<div id="v580.3.24"><span class="G1492 s">Knowing</span><span class="G3754 s"> that</span><span class="G575 s"> of</span><span class="G2962 s"> the Lord</span><span class="G618 s"> ye shall receive</span><span class="G469 s"> the reward</span><span class="G2817 s"> of the inheritance</span><span class="G1063 s">: for</span><span class="G1398 s"> ye serve</span><span class="G2962 s"> the Lord</span><span class="G5547 s"> Christ</span>.</div>
